in a fucking cage.

1:12:12.961 --> 1:12:14.330
Get in.

1:12:16.297 --> 1:12:18.100
[engine starts]

1:12:19.567 --> 1:12:21.069
[Al] Guess what.

1:12:21.203 --> 1:12:24.540
A cage is exactly what you're in
until you find this prick.

1:12:27.375 --> 1:12:29.811
