1:12:30.412 --> 1:12:32.047
You all right? Yeah.

1:12:32.414 --> 1:12:34.383
Hey, Norm. Hi.

1:12:37.152 --> 1:12:39.888
[exhales] Hello!
Oh, my God.

1:12:40.021 --> 1:12:43.291
You're a lifesaver, man. I got it.
My pleasure.

1:12:43.425 --> 1:12:44.693
[sighs]

1:12:44.827 --> 1:12:46.461
So they can't find us here?

1:12:46.594 --> 1:12:48.897
Trust me.
This is so much better
than a hotel.

1:12:49.030 --> 1:12:52.367
