with you till I get back, okay? Okay.

1:12:52.500 --> 1:12:54.570
I love you. I love you too.

1:13:01.910 --> 1:13:03.512
[sighs]

1:13:10.218 --> 1:13:11.520
[elevator bell dings]

1:13:15.724 --> 1:13:17.693
Well, what's this?
Where's this gonna go?

1:13:18.393 --> 1:13:19.494
Put that down.

1:13:19.628 --> 1:13:21.063
Where the hell
is my story?

1:13:21.196 --> 1:13:22.597
Hey. When did you get in?

1:13:22.730 --> 1:13:25.200
Léger told David Miller
to go fuck himself.

1:13:25.334 --> 1:13:27.603
The Sun didn't get
the article. I did.
I delivered.

1:13:27.736 --> 1:13:29.271
Where the fuck is
my front page, Art?

1:13:29.404 --> 1:13:31.640
Your junkie pal made some
pretty serious accusations.

