speaking in Thai]

1:50:05.798 --> 1:50:08.802
[Robert] Do you think
he could've organized
this transaction?

1:50:17.177 --> 1:50:18.244
Yeah.

1:50:18.377 --> 1:50:20.613
In the case number 635412,

1:50:20.747 --> 1:50:22.949
Thailand v. Daniel Léger,

1:50:23.482 --> 1:50:27.487
Judge Wanian finds the defendant
guilty of co-possession,

1:50:27.620 --> 1:50:29.622
along with Nipa Seangtong,

1:50:29.755 --> 1:50:32.559
Pimpan Seangtong
and Pracha Seangtong,

1:50:32.692 --> 1:50:35.261
of more than
200 grams of heroin.

1:50:35.394 --> 1:50:40.933
Therefore,
the defendant's sentence
is death by execution.

1:50:41.634 --> 1:50:43.736
The court will now
give the defendant

1:50:43.870 --> 1:50:45.905
a chance to change his plea.

1:50:46.806 --> 1:50:50.276
Does the defendant
wish to change his plea?

1:50:58.050 --> 1:50:59.318
Yes.

1:50:59.552 --> 1:51:01.254
What is your plea?

1:51:02.755 --> 1:51:04.190
Guilty.

1:51:05.492 --> 1:51:10.263
The sentence is
therefore changed
to 100 years of imprisonment.

1:51:14.667 --> 1:51:17.337
You've done a good thing,
Mr. Malarek.

1:51:17.470 --> 1:51:20.540
Without you, Léger
wouldn't stand a chance
against those guys.

1:51:20.673 --> 1:51:22.375
And he stands
a chance now?

1:51:22.508 --> 1:51:25.611
Those officers broke
nearly every procedure
and regulation there is.

1:51:25.745 --> 1:51:29.082
Let's hope you can move fast.
The average prisoner
doesn't last 10 years in there.

1:51:29.215 --> 1:51:31.051
Half of that
for a Westerner.

1:51:31.717 --> 1:51:33.286
This is my priority.

1:51:33.986 --> 1:51:35.688
Thanks, man. Yeah.

1:51:35.821 --> 1:51:37.290
Take care.

1:51:37.423 --> 1:51:39.025
Good luck!

1:51:39.159 --> 1:51:40.927
[door opens]

1:51:42.662 --> 1:51:44.164
[whispering] Hey.

1:51:45.898 --> 1:51:48.201
Uh, she's-- she's gone.

1:51:50.603 --> 1:51:52.071
What do you mean,
she's gone?

1:51:52.204 --> 1:51:54.773
I-I got your message
and came home,

1:51:54.907 --> 1:51:56.209
but there was
no one here.

1:51:56.342 --> 1:51:58.011
She-- Sh-She's gone.

1:52:09.389 --> 1:52:10.790
Anna?

1:52:17.230 --> 1:52:18.798
[sighs]

1:52:19.231 --> 1:52:22.202
[beeping]

1:52:22.935 --> 1:52:25.238
[line ringing]

1:52:25.371 --> 1:52:26.539
[ringing]

1:52:26.673 --> 1:52:27.974
Hello?

1:52:28.107 --> 1:52:30.443
Denise, put Anna
on the phone, please.

1:52:30.576 --> 1:52:32.045
She's not here.

1:52:33.679 --> 1:52:34.948
Do you know where she is?

1:52:35.081 --> 1:52:37.416
No. Don't fuck with me, Denise.

1:52:37.549 --> 1:52:40.286
If you know where she is,
I need to know now. All right?

1:52:40.419 --> 1:52:43.790
I'm really scared that
something's happened to them. She'll call you.

1:52:44.557 --> 1:52:46.526
[dial tone]

1:53:00.339 --> 1:53:01.507
Happy see you.

1:53:01.641 --> 1:53:03.409
Yeah, bet you are.

1:53:05.044 --> 1:53:06.345
What are those?

1:53:06.479 --> 1:53:07.981
Guard left them for you.

1:53:19.125 --> 1:53:20.527
This is from my mother.

1:53:24.797 --> 1:53:27.000
Those fuckers
kept these from me?

1:53:30.303 --> 1:53:31.504
What's this?

1:53:34.940 --> 1:53:37.143
"Public Complaints Commission."

1:53:38.478 --> 1:53:41.447
They're investigating
my case back home.

1:53:41.581 --> 1:53:44.250
Holy shit!
They're coming here to see me.

1:53:44.384 --> 1:53:46.452
Lucky. Lucky you.

1:53:46.586 --> 1:53:48.087
Shit, shit, shit.

1:53:48.220 --> 1:53:50.189
I need to sign this form
against the federal police

1:53:50.323 --> 1:53:52.091
and send it
back to them.

1:53:52.625 --> 1:53:54.193
Need contact
in mail room.

1:53:54.327 --> 1:53:56.428
Yeah, no shit.
I'm fucked!

1:53:56.929 --> 1:53:58.965
I don't have any money
for a contact.

1:53:59.732 --> 1:54:02.502
Already got good contact.

1:54:03.335 --> 1:54:04.503
Who?

1:54:04.904 --> 1:54:06.339
In the yard.

1:54:06.472 --> 1:54:09.575
Back, back, left.
Behind the kitchen.

1:54:10.443 --> 1:54:14.580
You see Tuan.
He high, not working.

1:54:15.214 --> 1:54:18.117
Tuan. The junkie.
He delivered this?

1:54:19.518 --> 1:54:23.389
Holy shit, you fat-ass
Buddhist motherfucker.

1:54:26.759 --> 1:54:28.995
[beeping]

1:54:32.865 --> 1:54:35.334
[phone ringing] [inhales sharply]

1:54:35.735 --> 1:54:37.469
Mmm. Hello?

1:54:37.770 --> 1:54:39.339
Anna?

1:54:42.508 --> 1:54:44.110
Anna, is that you?

1:54:49.115 --> 1:54:51.817
Okay, sweetheart,
I know you don't want
to talk to me right now,

1:54:51.951 --> 1:54:53.887
and I-- I get it.

1:54:54.987 --> 1:54:56.456
I, uh...

1:54:57.757 --> 1:54:59.592
I just...

1:55:02.161 --> 1:55:06.132
You and our daughter
come first.

1:55:08.868 --> 1:55:11.304
I don't care about TV shows

1:55:11.437 --> 1:55:15.074
or newspapers
or investigations

1:55:15.207 --> 1:55:20.146
or anything else nearly as much
as I care about you two.

1:55:24.149 --> 1:55:26.185
Let me prove that to you.

1:55:29.054 --> 1:55:32.492
And then, and only then...

1:55:35.161 --> 1:55:37.397
maybe you'll let me
save the world.

1:55:41.600 --> 1:55:45.038
Maybe just a little,
itty-bitty part of the world.

1:55:46.905 --> 1:55:48.441
[chuckles]

1:55:52.044 --> 1:55:53.513
Anna?

1:55:54.813 --> 1:55:56.582
We're at my sister's.

1:55:57.850 --> 1:55:59.319
I knew that.

1:56:00.118 --> 1:56:01.654
Are you coming?

1:56:03.122 --> 1:56:04.557
Right away.

1:56:04.691 --> 1:56:08.227
[man singing in Thai on PA]

1:56:16.702 --> 1:56:18.304
[speaking Thai]

1:56:30.916 --> 1:56:33.519
[in Thai]

1:57:14.694 --> 1:57:16.229
Okay, I think I'm ready.

1:57:20.198 --> 1:57:23.736
Right around here?
Make sure you get as much
of the background as possible.

1:57:23.869 --> 1:57:25.270
Can you count me in?

1:57:26.004 --> 1:57:28.174
[cameraman]
Three, two, one.

1:57:28.307 --> 1:57:30.276
It's a big day
for Daniel Léger,

1:57:30.409 --> 1:57:32.378
the Canadian man
who was wrongly accused

1:57:32.511 --> 1:57:35.548
of smuggling heroin
in Thailand in 1989.

1:57:35.681 --> 1:57:39.118
His plane landed on home soil
just a few moments ago.

1:57:39.618 --> 1:57:41.353
He was escorted off by officers,

1:57:41.486 --> 1:57:43.456
who will then accompany him
to a Canadian prison,

1:57:43.589 --> 1:57:45.725
where he will finally
be released on parole.

1:57:45.858 --> 1:57:47.926
Léger, who beat his heroin
addiction on his own,

1:57:48.060 --> 1:57:50.429
was able to mount a defense
against the federal government

1:57:50.562 --> 1:57:53.833
from his cell in Bangkok by
gathering thousands of documents

1:57:53.966 --> 1:57:56.769
through the public access
to government information
in Ottawa.

1:57:56.902 --> 1:57:59.471
Léger was able to
secure himself a transfer

1:57:59.604 --> 1:58:02.308
to serve his time
in his country.

1:58:02.675 --> 1:58:04.143
Actually, right now,

1:58:04.276 --> 1:58:07.946
Daniel Léger is being
brought from the terminal.

1:58:08.380 --> 1:58:10.183
[whispering] In on him.

1:58:22.295 --> 1:58:24.230
Welcome home,
Mr. Léger.

1:58:24.730 --> 1:58:25.997
Thank you.

1:58:26.732 --> 1:58:29.302
I notice that no one
is here to meet you.

1:58:29.802 --> 1:58:31.137
I, uh...

1:58:31.737 --> 1:58:34.907
I lost both my parents
while I was in prison.

1:58:35.040 --> 1:58:36.609
Ah. I'm really
sorry to hear that.

1:58:36.742 --> 1:58:38.977
Hey, guys, do you mind
just giving us two seconds?

1:58:39.111 --> 1:58:41.580
Two seconds, please?
Thank you. Uh...

1:58:42.080 --> 1:58:46.218
It took great courage for you
to be able to build your case
from a prison cell in Bangkok.

1:58:46.352 --> 1:58:48.254
How did you manage
to do that?

1:58:49.888 --> 1:58:51.456
Zen Buddhism.

1:58:52.524 --> 1:58:54.894
Do you know what happened
to the federal police

1:58:55.027 --> 1:58:56.829
that, uh,
that arrested you?

1:58:58.163 --> 1:58:59.799
No, no idea. No?

1:58:59.932 --> 1:59:02.501
They were given medals
for their work
on Operation Goliath

1:59:02.634 --> 1:59:04.403
and they were
awarded desk jobs.

1:59:04.536 --> 1:59:06.739
How does that
make you feel?

1:59:06.872 --> 1:59:11.210
I mean, do you feel
like you've been cheated out of
eight years of your life?

1:59:13.779 --> 1:59:15.448
Obviously, there's no words
that can describe

1:59:15.581 --> 1:59:17.182
what Daniel Léger is-- Grateful.

1:59:17.816 --> 1:59:21.587
You ask me how I feel.
I feel grateful.

1:59:25.191 --> 1:59:26.759
Thank you, Victor.

1:59:29.995 --> 1:59:31.564
Did you get that?

1:59:36.969 --> 1:59:38.538
And cut.
